dex funds used to manage a portion of market risk arising from", "bbox": [93.8, 446.7, 1169.0, 465.4]}, {"text": "our deferred compensation liability. The fair value of our debt obligations as of December 31, 2011 and December 25, 2010 was $29.8 billion", "bbox": [93.8, 471.7, 1159.8, 490.4]}, {"text": "and $25.9 billion, respectively, based upon prices of similar instruments in the marketplace.", "bbox": [93.8, 496.7, 788.4, 515.4]}, {"text": "Note 11", "bbox": [596.4, 559.1, 660.3, 577.9]}, {"text": "Net Income Attributable to PepsiCo per Common Share", "bbox": [334.5, 587.8, 922.1, 612.8]}, {"text": "Basic net income attributable to PepsiCo per common share is net income available for PepsiCo common shareholders divided by the", "bbox": [93.8, 642.5, 1117.8, 661.3]}, {"text": "weighted average of common shares outstanding during the period. Diluted net income attributable to PepsiCo per common share is calcu-", "bbox": [93.8, 667.5, 1166.6, 686.3]}, {"text": "lated using the weighted average of common shares outstanding adjusted to include the effect that would occur if in- the-money employee", "bbox": [93.8, 692.5, 1166.5, 711.3]}, {"text": "stock options were exercised and RSUs and preferred shares were converted into common shares. Options to purchase 25.9 million shares in", "bbox": [93.8, 717.5, 1168.0, 736.3]}, {"text": "2011, 24.4 million shares in 2010 and 39.0 million shares in 2009 were not included in the calculation of diluted earnings per common share", "bbox": [93.8, 742.5, 1152.8, 761.3]}, {"text": "because these options were out- of-the- money. Out- of-the- money options had average exercise prices of $66.99 in 2011, $67.26 in 2010 and", "bbox": [93.8, 767.5, 1158.6, 786.3]}, {"text": "$61.52 in 2009.", "bbox": [93.8, 792.5, 206.5, 811.3]}, {"text": "The computations of basic and diluted net income attributable to PepsiCo per common share are as follows:", "bbox": [112.5, 817.5, 938.6, 836.2]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [661.2, 848.5, 689.3, 863.1]